{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-template-tsx","path":"/css-viewport/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/4fae8/css-viewport-thumbnail.webp 256w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/2bf0f/css-viewport-thumbnail.webp 512w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/4c79d/css-viewport-thumbnail.webp 680w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/e3135/css-viewport-thumbnail.png 256w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/06341/css-viewport-thumbnail.png 512w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/ca1dc/css-viewport-thumbnail.png 680w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/ca1dc/css-viewport-thumbnail.png\"\n            alt=\"CSS-viewport-thumbnail\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">CSS-viewport-thumbnail</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>개요</h2>\n<p>웹사이트를 모바일이나 태블릿 화면에서 제공할 때의 문제점을 다들 겪어봤을 것입니다.</p>\n<p>100vh로 지정하더라도, 툴바, 주소 표시줄의 UI가 표시되어 계획했던 크기와 맞지 않는 문제입니다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위한 viewport 단위를 알아보겠습니다</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/viewport-unit-variants\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://caniuse.com/viewport-unit-variants</a></p>\n<p>Google 크롬, Microsoft Edge, Safari, Firefox 및 주요 브라우저는 지원됩니다.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.0625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/4fae8/dvh.webp 256w,\n/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/2bf0f/dvh.webp 512w,\n/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/cf465/dvh.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/e3135/dvh.png 256w,\n/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/06341/dvh.png 512w,\n/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/78d47/dvh.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a67204f5281694311c5c3f290b532098/78d47/dvh.png\"\n            alt=\"vh image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">vh image</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>본론</h2>\n<h3>1. dvh (Dynamic  <strong>Viewport Height)</strong></h3>\n<p>dvh는 주소 표시줄이 노출이 되고, 안되고 상관 없이 현재 보여지는 뷰포트 높이를 동적으로 가져옵니다.</p>\n<p>dvh를 모든 브라우저에서 사용가능한 것은 아니므로, 이전 브라우저도 대응하기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">100nh</code>도 병행해 작성하는 것이 좋습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>foo <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 100vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 100dvh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>2. svh (Short Viewport Height)</h3>\n<p>svh는 사용자 화면 기준으로 가장 짧은 뷰포트 값을 가져옵니다.</p>\n<p>주소 표시줄이 없어져도 기존 주소표시줄의 높이 값을 뺀 나머지 값을 가져옵니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>foo <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 100vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 100svh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>3. lvh (Large Viewport Height)</h3>\n<p>lvh는 svh와는 반대로 사용자 화면 기준으로 가장 긴 뷰표트 값을 가져온다.</p>\n<p>주소 표시줄이 있더라도 주소 표시줄이 없을 때의 총 화면의 길이를 가져온다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>foo <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 100vh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 100lvh<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>가로폭에서도 똑같이 「svw, lvw, dvw」 단위를 지정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>그 외, vi(svi, lvi, dvi) 등 인라인 방향의 viewport의 사이즈나, vb(svb, lvb, dvb)와 같은 블록 방향의 viewport의 사이즈의 단위도 있습니다.</p>\n<h3>참고</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://blanche-toile.com/web/large-small-and-dynamic-viewport-units\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://blanche-toile.com/web/large-small-and-dynamic-viewport-units</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[CSS] 모바일 100vh 문제 해결 - dvh, svh, lvh","summary":"모바일 화면에서 100vh로 지정했을 때 표시줄때문에 생긴 문제의 해결방안을 알아보자.","date":"2024.08.06.","categories":["CSS","error"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/34aa0/css-viewport-thumbnail.png","srcSet":"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/ba84f/css-viewport-thumbnail.png 170w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/306c9/css-viewport-thumbnail.png 340w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/34aa0/css-viewport-thumbnail.png 680w","sizes":"(min-width: 680px) 680px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/85dcc/css-viewport-thumbnail.webp 170w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/d5c2b/css-viewport-thumbnail.webp 340w,\n/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/4c15c/css-viewport-thumbnail.webp 680w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 680px) 680px, 100vw"}]},"width":680,"height":680}},"publicURL":"/static/194c1660f8051c36f63020995b4733c6/css-viewport-thumbnail.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css-viewport/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}